---
// About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="about-section section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">About <span class="text-gradient">&nbsp;Me</span></h2>
            <div class="about-grid reveal">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>Hello! I am an infrastructure-focused engineer with practical experience managing Linux-based
                        systems and communication platforms. I enjoy building reliable systems and learning modern
                        DevOps tools to improve automation, scalability, and service delivery.</p>
                    <p>My goal is to become a DevOps engineer and build scalable cloud infrastructure platforms for
                        hosting services such as email, VoIP, and cloud applications.</p>

                    <h3 class="skills-title">My core expertise includes:</h3>
                    <ul class="skills-list">
                        <li>Linux Server Administration</li>
                        <li>Proxmox Virtualization</li>
                        <li>VoIP (Issabel/Asterisk)</li>
                        <li>Postfix, Zimbra, cPanel</li>
                        <li>DNS & Mail Records</li>
                        <li>Docker & CI/CD Concepts</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Decorative element or image placeholder -->
                <div class="about-image-container">
                    <div class="about-image-placeholder glass-card">
                        <img src="images/profile.jpg" alt="Rakibul Hasan Rizvi" class="profile-img" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>